---
title: "{{ title }}"
date: {{ date_iso }}
draft: false
description: "{{ description }}"
tags: ["weekly", "market", "review"]
---

## 📊 週間サマリー（{{ week_label }}）

<div class="market-grid">
<div class="market-card">

### 🇺🇸 米国市場（週間騰落率）

{% for idx in us_indices %}
<div class="market-row">
<span class="market-name">{{ idx.display_name }}</span>
<span class="market-value">
  {%- if idx.error -%}
  <span style="color:gray;">取得失敗</span>
  {%- else -%}
  {{ "%.2f"|format(idx.close) if idx.close else "—" }}
  <span class="{{ 'change-positive' if idx.week_change_pct and idx.week_change_pct > 0 else 'change-negative' if idx.week_change_pct and idx.week_change_pct < 0 else 'change-neutral' }}">
    {{ "%+.2f%%"|format(idx.week_change_pct) if idx.week_change_pct is not none else "—" }}（週間）
  </span>
  {%- endif -%}
</span>
</div>
{% endfor %}

</div>
<div class="market-card">

### 🇯🇵 日本市場（週間騰落率）

{% for idx in jp_indices %}
<div class="market-row">
<span class="market-name">{{ idx.display_name }}</span>
<span class="market-value">
  {%- if idx.error -%}
  <span style="color:gray;">取得失敗</span>
  {%- else -%}
  {{ "%.2f"|format(idx.close) if idx.close else "—" }}
  <span class="{{ 'change-positive' if idx.week_change_pct and idx.week_change_pct > 0 else 'change-negative' if idx.week_change_pct and idx.week_change_pct < 0 else 'change-neutral' }}">
    {{ "%+.2f%%"|format(idx.week_change_pct) if idx.week_change_pct is not none else "—" }}（週間）
  </span>
  {%- endif -%}
</span>
</div>
{% endfor %}

</div>
</div>

### 📊 週間の主要指標

<div class="indicators-row">
{% for ind in indicators %}
<div class="indicator-item">
<span class="indicator-label">{{ ind.display_name }}</span>
<span class="indicator-value">
  {%- if ind.error -%}—
  {%- elif ind.name == "USDJPY" -%}{{ "%.2f"|format(ind.value) if ind.value else "—" }}
  {%- elif ind.name == "US10Y" -%}{{ "%.2f%%"|format(ind.value) if ind.value else "—" }}
  {%- else -%}{{ "%.2f"|format(ind.value) if ind.value else "—" }}{% if ind.signal is defined %} {{ ind.signal }}{% endif %}
  {%- endif -%}
</span>
{% if ind.week_change_pct is defined and ind.week_change_pct is not none %}
<span class="indicator-label {{ 'change-positive' if ind.week_change_pct > 0 else 'change-negative' if ind.week_change_pct < 0 else 'change-neutral' }}">
  週間: {{ "%+.2f%%"|format(ind.week_change_pct) }}
</span>
{% endif %}
</div>
{% endfor %}

{%- if fear_greed and not fear_greed.error %}
<div class="indicator-item">
<span class="indicator-label">Fear & Greed</span>
<span class="indicator-value">{{ fear_greed.score }} {{ fear_greed.emoji }}</span>
<span class="indicator-label">{{ fear_greed.label }}</span>
</div>
{%- endif %}
</div>

{%- if sector_data and not sector_data.error %}
---

### 🏭 週間セクター騰落ランキング

<table class="tech-table">
<thead>
<tr><th>順位</th><th>セクター</th><th>ETF</th><th>週間騰落率</th></tr>
</thead>
<tbody>
{% for s in sector_data.sectors %}
<tr>
<td>{{ s.rank }}</td>
<td>{{ s.name }}</td>
<td style="font-size:0.8rem;color:gray;">{{ s.ticker }}</td>
<td class="{{ 'change-positive' if s.change_pct and s.change_pct > 0 else 'change-negative' if s.change_pct and s.change_pct < 0 else 'change-neutral' }}">
  {%- if s.error -%}—{%- else -%}{{ "%+.2f%%"|format(s.change_pct) if s.change_pct is not none else "—" }}{%- endif -%}
</td>
</tr>
{% endfor %}
</tbody>
</table>
{%- endif %}

{%- if direction_score %}
---

### 🧭 週末時点の方向性

<div class="indicators-row">
<div class="indicator-item">
<span class="indicator-label">米国</span>
<span class="indicator-value">{{ direction_score.us.emoji }} {{ direction_score.us.label }}</span>
</div>
<div class="indicator-item">
<span class="indicator-label">日本</span>
<span class="indicator-value">{{ direction_score.jp.emoji }} {{ direction_score.jp.label }}</span>
</div>
<div class="indicator-item">
<span class="indicator-label">総合</span>
<span class="indicator-value">{{ direction_score.overall.emoji }} {{ direction_score.overall.label }}</span>
</div>
</div>
{%- endif %}

---

### 📰 週間注目ニュース

{% if news_error %}
<p style="color:gray;">ニュース取得失敗</p>
{% elif news_top5 %}
<ol class="news-list">
{% for item in news_top5 %}
<li>
{% if item.url %}<a href="{{ item.url }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener">{{ item.title }}</a>{% else %}{{ item.title }}{% endif %}
<span class="news-source">（{{ item.source }}）</span>
</li>
{% endfor %}
</ol>
{% else %}
<p style="color:gray;">ニュースなし</p>
{% endif %}

---

### 📅 来週の重要イベント

{% if calendar_events %}
<ul class="calendar-list">
{% for ev in calendar_events %}
<li>
<span class="calendar-date">{{ ev.date_str }}({{ ev.weekday }})</span>
<span>{{ "🇺🇸" if ev.country == "US" else "🇯🇵" if ev.country == "JP" else "" }} {{ ev.event }}</span>
{% if ev.importance == "high" %}<span style="color:#ef4444;font-size:0.75rem;"> ★重要</span>{% endif %}
</li>
{% endfor %}
</ul>
{% else %}
<p style="color:gray;">来週のイベントなし</p>
{% endif %}

---

<p style="font-size:0.75rem;color:gray;">
生成日時: {{ generated_at }} | データ: yfinance / RSS
</p>
